---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import { roofingAsphalt, ctaAssistant } from '../../../lib/images';
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AnnouncementBar from '../../../components/AnnouncementBar.astro';
import Navbar from '../../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Hero from '../../../components/Hero.astro';
import LogoSlider from '../../../components/LogoSlider.astro';
import FAQ from '../../../components/FAQ.astro';
import ContactUs from '../../../components/ContactUs.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';

const city = 'Fremont';
const county = 'Alameda County';
const adjective = 'Dedicated';
---

<Layout
  title={`${adjective} ADU Contractors in ${city}, CA | Hamilton Exteriors`}
  description={`Hamilton Exteriors provides ${adjective.toLowerCase()} ADU contractors in ${city}, CA. Expert design, permits, and construction. Call for a free consultation!`}
>
  <AnnouncementBar />
  <Navbar />
  <Hero
    formTitle={`Get a FREE Estimate in ${city}`}
    headline={`${adjective} ADU Contractors in ${city}, CA`}
  />
  <LogoSlider />

  <!-- Why Choose Section -->
  <section class="w-full bg-white py-12 md:py-32 lg:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-5 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <div class="hidden lg:block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <Image src={roofingAsphalt} alt="Hamilton Exteriors ADU project" width={1200} height={900} class="w-full h-auto object-cover" style="aspect-ratio: 632/478;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div>
      <h2 style="font-family: 'THE BOLD FONT (FREE VERSION)', 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(13, 43, 29); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Why Choose Hamilton Exteriors as Your {adjective} ADU Contractors in {city}, CA?
      </h2>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(13, 43, 29); margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Reliable. Skilled. Proven.
      </h3>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Hamilton Exteriors provides dedicated ADU contractors in Fremont, CA who bring focused attention to every project in this thriving South Bay city. Fremont's generous lot sizes in neighborhoods like Mission San Jose, Niles, and Warm Springs make it one of the best cities in Alameda County for ADU construction, and our team knows exactly how to maximize that potential.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        We manage every detail of your ADU build from site evaluation and design through permitting and final walkthrough. Our dedication means we stay involved at every phase, coordinating with the City of Fremont's planning department and ensuring your project meets all current building codes and ADU regulations without costly delays.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Whether you're building an ADU for aging parents, a young adult returning home, or rental income near the BART corridor, our team delivers quality construction on schedule and within budget.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
            <strong style="color: rgb(13, 43, 29);">Expert Design</strong> — Custom ADU plans designed to maximize your property's potential while complementing the architectural character of your neighborhood.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
            <strong style="color: rgb(13, 43, 29);">Permit Handling</strong> — We manage the entire city permitting process from application to approval, eliminating the delays and confusion that come from navigating it yourself.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
            <strong style="color: rgb(13, 43, 29);">Quality Materials</strong> — Premium construction materials selected for durability, energy efficiency, and long-term value that stand up to the Bay Area's unique climate conditions.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
            <strong style="color: rgb(13, 43, 29);">Clear Communication</strong> — You'll always know where your project stands with regular updates and responsive communication throughout every phase of construction.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why ADU Contractors Section -->
  <section class="w-full bg-cream py-12 md:py-32 lg:py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px] px-5 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-start">
      <div>
      <h2 style="font-family: 'THE BOLD FONT (FREE VERSION)', 'Oswald', sans-serif; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(13, 43, 29); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Why {adjective} ADU Contractors in {city}, CA Are Essential?
      </h2>
      <h3 style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: rgb(13, 43, 29); margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Space. Value. Flexibility.
      </h3>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Fremont is the fourth-largest city in the Bay Area, and its growing population has driven housing demand to record levels. ADUs give Fremont homeowners a smart way to add square footage without the cost and hassle of moving. With strong rental demand driven by proximity to Tesla's factory, tech employers along the 880 corridor, and excellent schools, a well-built ADU can generate meaningful monthly income.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105); margin-bottom: 16px;">
        Dedicated ADU contractors matter in Fremont because the city's permitting process requires detailed plans that comply with specific lot coverage ratios, parking requirements, and utility connection standards. A contractor who knows Fremont's rules can avoid the rejected plans and re-submissions that cost homeowners weeks of delays and thousands in additional fees.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 17px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(104, 104, 105);">
        With a dedicated team managing your project from concept to completion, you get a finished ADU that adds real value to your property and gives your family the flexible living space you need in one of the East Bay's most desirable communities.
      </p>
      </div>
      <div class="hidden lg:block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <Image src={ctaAssistant} alt="Hamilton Exteriors construction crew" width={1200} height={900} class="w-full h-auto object-cover" style="aspect-ratio: 632/626;" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <FAQ />
  <ContactUs />
  <Footer />
</Layout>
